reviewText: Even with a code free player half of the DVD's won't run (error no disc or not running smoothly). Annoying.
Make sure you have the correct DVD to play! We ultimately play these on our Mac computer.
Perfect for toddlers. Each disc offers continuous play with no need for advancing episodes manually.
Don't work in the US. Why sell it to us if it won't work? Now I have to deal with a crying child.
Bought for a Christmas present for my children who grew up watching Peppa!!!
